## Low Severity

### 9. General Fixture — `_logger` field
```csharp
private FakeLogger _logger = null!;
// initialized in [TestInitialize] but never used by any test
```
**Problem:** Every test pays the cost of constructing `_logger` for nothing. It also misleads readers into thinking logging is part of the tested behavior.
**Fix:** Remove `_logger` from the shared setup. Add it only in tests that actually need it.

